On count 1, Sentence is withheld and the defendant is placed on probation to DOC for nine (9) years.
On counts 2-5, sentence is withheld and the defendant is placed on probation to DOC for seven (7) years.
Conditions of probation:
1) Assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Departments assessment process;
2) Pay restitution of $30,625.83 to Harvey Clark at a minimum of $35.00 per month;
3) Defendant is to make a full financial disclosure statement to the Department of Corrections in order for them to assess and monitor her finances;
4) Defendant is to have no contact with Harvey Clark unless approved by her agent and approved by Harvey;
5) Send apology letter to the victim after its approved by the agent;
6) Defendant is prohibited from engaging in any gaming;
7) Defendant is to have no contact with any establishment/facilities which offer any gaming or gambling or any sort;
8) Pay court costs;
9) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
10) provide DNA sample and pay the surcharge;
11) spend twelve (12) months in the county jail, under the Huber Law, on count 1 only, commencing on 11-27-15 by 6:00 p.m.
Minutes.
